cu.explanation_en: Setting tracking_area_code to an out-of-range value 99999 will cause TAC validation errors, leading to configuration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting tracking_area_code to an out-of-range value 99999 will cause TAC validation errors, leading to configuration rejection.
du.explanation_zh: 將 tracking_area_code 設定為超出範圍的值 99999 會導致 TAC 驗證錯誤，造成配置拒絕。
